    },
    {
      "id": "quote:80b8228fa2dbc56b",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 296,
        "char_start": 189,
        "episode_id": "ep-2a703b6f57d9020f",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-02",
        "text": "Thanks, Rina. Excited for this one \u2014 wreck-diving fundamentals is something I've been thinking about a lot.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 12000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 6000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p03_e01.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:b1127543a0359905",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 507,
        "char_start": 303,
        "episode_id": "ep-2a703b6f57d9020f",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "Before we dive in, a quick word from our sponsor Suunto. Suunto builds dive computers and outdoor watches that you trust because they don't quit when conditions change. Use code POD for an extended trial.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 18000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 12000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p03_e01.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:675b4b28a3a9c0eb",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 593,
        "char_start": 507,
        "episode_id": "ep-2a703b6f57d9020f",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "What does that look like day-to-day? What's the most underrated piece of wreck diving?",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 24000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 18000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p03_e01.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:5f33ab8a9a787c50",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 821,
        "char_start": 601,
        "episode_id": "ep-2a703b6f57d9020f",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-02",
        "text": "Yeah, so \u2014 Wreck penetration is a planning problem first, a buoyancy problem second. The dive happens at the desk. We've seen this play out at teams using Suunto. And the second-order effect is the part most people miss.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 30000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 24000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p03_e01.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
